{"id":396,"ayahs":[{"number":85,"arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِى فَرَضَ عَلَيْكَ ٱلْقُرْءَانَ لَرَآدُّكَ إِلَىٰ مَعَادٍۢ ۚ قُل رَّبِّىٓ أَعْلَمُ مَن جَآءَ بِٱلْهُدَىٰ وَمَنْ هُوَ فِى ضَلَٰلٍۢ مُّبِينٍۢ","translation":"VERILY, [O believer,] He who has laid down this Qur’an in plain terms, making it binding on thee, will assuredly bring thee back [from death] to a life renewed. Say [unto those who reject the truth]: My Sus­tainer knows best, as to who is right-guided and who is obviously lost in error!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3337.mp3","surahId":28,"words":[{"id":66249,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"(হে নাবী) নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66250,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66251,"position":3,"arabic":"فَرَضَ","translation":"ফরজ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66252,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَيْكَ","translation":"উপর তোমার","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66253,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","translation":"(এই) কুরআন","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66254,"position":6,"arabic":"لَرَآدُّكَ","translation":"অবশ্যই তোমাকে ফিরিয়ে আনবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66255,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66256,"position":8,"arabic":"مَعَادٍۢ ۚ","translation":"প্রত্যাবর্তনস্হলের","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66258,"position":9,"arabic":"قُل","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66259,"position":10,"arabic":"رَّبِّىٓ","translation":"\"আমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":66260,"position":11,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","translation":"খুব জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/028_085_012.mp3","charTypeN